item.title: Wacky small planes
item.dc:creator: Brian Kirsten
item.content:encoded:
A small plane carrying gubernatorial candidate Max Linn made an emergency landing on Interstate 4 this afternoon, causing a massive traffic jam in the eastbound lanes from Florida's Turnpike to South Orange Blossom Trail, Orlando Police said.
Link to Orlando Sentinel article.
